videos.headline: TCU's Reagor leaps for grab, races for 67-yard TD
videos.description: TCU QB Michael Collins drops the snap, but airs it out to Jalen Reagor, who comes down with it and sprints past Kansas State defenders for a 67-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kansas State's Delton throws 21-yard TD strike
videos.description: Kansas State QB Alex Delton throws a strike Malik Knowles at the back of the end zone for a 21-yard touchdown vs. TCU.
